   Monday's Markets:
   Stocks Rise,
   Bonds End
   Unchanged
   ---
   Pre-Holiday Trading
   Is Thin; Dollar Sinks
   As Commodities Gain
   ----
   By Christopher Winans
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
